      <title>随着奈拉沉没，尼日利亚正在就高达 15 亿美元的援助进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/nigeria-in-world-bank-talks-for-up-to-1-5-billion-of-budget-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚正在讨论世界银行提供多达 15 亿美元的资金，以帮助缓解导致奈拉急剧贬值的美元严重短缺问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/nigeria-in-world-bank-talks-for-up-to-1-5-billion-of-budget-aid</guid>
